I gave it all I had, but these Hella Hot Outstanding Puffs just lit me up and my guy @lewishowes made sure I got cooled off with the quickness. S/O to @javalemcgee for all the great work he’s doing with his charity @juglifewater. 

I challenge @chriswharder, @edmylett & @mhiggins to the #HellaHotChallenge, a partnership between @outstandingfoods and @juglifewater to help raise awareness and encourage donations to bring clean drinking water to communities that need it most around the world. @outstandingfoods is matching all donations up to $10k 

Here's how you can participate:
1. Grab a friend, a cup of water and your Hella Hot Outstanding Puffs 🔥
2. Set up your camera and give your friend the cup of water 🚰
3. As soon as the 30 second timer begins, your friend becomes the judge. Hit go and start snacking, but keep that poker face! 😐
4. The second you crack, they get to throw the cup of water in your face… but, if you can last the full 30 seconds — snag that cup and throw the water on them 💦
5. When time is up (and one of you is wet), tell us the three or more people you’re challenging! 🏆
6. Post the video to your Instagram feed and/or TikTok and use the hashtag #HellaHotChallenge and tag both @outstandingfoods and @juglifewater as well as the 3+ others you challenged.

To learn more about the challenge hit the link in my bio and get involved 🙌🙌

Let’s keep pushing this mental health conversation. I challenge @lewishowes to #saysomething

node.text: We had an amazing family adventure this week in beautiful Orlando, Florida. After her birthday @bryianadyrdek qualified to compete for the World’s Perfect Woman title. She won the title of World’s Perfect Miss when we were dating many years ago, so she had to wait till she turned 30 to be able to compete for another title. We brought the family out including @patdyr, @genedyrdek1940, and @secabrown to cheer her on. It was so much fun for us to watch her get back in the game she loves so much. So proud of her. In my opinion she won this title easy, but the judges did not seem to think so… maybe I’m biased, but don’t forget I judged Miss Universe back in 2014. Truth is she was, is, and will always be, World’s Perfect Woman to us.

node.text:
I sent this text to @brian_atlas the President of @sls in the summer of 2016. I had been watching @yutohorigome footage on Instagram and knew he was a special talent. I wanted to get him in into Street League, so I sent this text and it would take another year before it would eventually happen. Throughout the years as Yuto became a true superstar and contest champion, I always thought about this text as I knew it was some over the top bold prediction about him. It’s way more bold than I remembered. Congrats Yuto on fulfilling your destiny and making me look like Nostradamus!

S/O to everyone that made Olympic Skateboarding possible. From Gary Ream to @joeciaglia to @tonyhawk. It was a beautiful moment for me to watch the format we created at @sls come alive on the world stage.

📸 @atibaphoto

node.text: Happy Birthday to my amazing wife @bryianadyrdek! Thirty, Flirty, and Thriving was her vision for many years ahead of this milestone birthday and Thirty, Flirty, and Thriving is what she got. Skates, cakes, and plenty of balloons! It was so much fun. Cheers to a new decade of thriving 🥂Love you so much! 💘💘 💘💘💘💞💞💞💓💓💓💕💕💕💗💗💗💗💗💘💘💘💘💘

I gave it all I had, but these Hella Hot Outstanding Puffs just lit me up and my guy @lewishowes made sure I got cooled off with the quickness. S/O to @javalemcgee for all the great work he’s doing with his charity @juglifewater. 

I challenge @chriswharder, @edmylett & @mhiggins to the #HellaHotChallenge, a partnership between @outstandingfoods and @juglifewater to help raise awareness and encourage donations to bring clean drinking water to communities that need it most around the world. @outstandingfoods is matching all donations up to $10k 

Here's how you can participate:
1. Grab a friend, a cup of water and your Hella Hot Outstanding Puffs 🔥
2. Set up your camera and give your friend the cup of water 🚰
3. As soon as the 30 second timer begins, your friend becomes the judge. Hit go and start snacking, but keep that poker face! 😐
4. The second you crack, they get to throw the cup of water in your face… but, if you can last the full 30 seconds — snag that cup and throw the water on them 💦
5. When time is up (and one of you is wet), tell us the three or more people you’re challenging! 🏆
6. Post the video to your Instagram feed and/or TikTok and use the hashtag #HellaHotChallenge and tag both @outstandingfoods and @juglifewater as well as the 3+ others you challenged.

To learn more about the challenge hit the link in my bio and get involved 🙌🙌

node.text:
Are you born an entrepreneur or do you become one? On this episode of #BuildwithRob this might be proof that you can be born one. My guest this week is the Natural Born Do-or-Dier @_matt.wan. Founder and CEO of @livemomentous, he was just eighteen when I helped him shape his vision for the worlds best supplement brand. Wise beyond his years, this young entrepreneur might as well be 40! 

@dyrdekmachine
